  "subject": "Populate HibernateConfiguration from application.yml",
  "commit_message": "Populate HibernateConfiguration from application.yml\n\nCps Session Manager throws a HibernateException at runtime, as the\nDB_HOST and DB_PORT variables are not available in hibernate.cfg.xml\n(Strangely integration tests work but it uses a separate xml)\n\n- Delete hibernate config files\n- Use a config bean to copy the settings from application.yml\n\nIssue-ID: CPS-2629\nSigned-off-by: danielhanrahan <daniel.hanrahan@est.tech>\nChange-Id: I298c902c46e6f7df33363a146ae4b47727184f79\n",
